{"title":"上帝的随手画","uid":"8f82e4e77dd7edc64fc9226125252469","slug":"graffiti-of-god","date":"2022-06-15T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-06-29T12:18:25.556Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/graffiti-of-god.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://s2.loli.net/2022/06/29/r4j9FThMy8RJEZt.png","content":"<p>这段时间我回到了武汉和同学与对象游玩。广州正值雨季，终日天色昏昏、雨水淅沥，而武汉却阳光正盛、热气灼灼。</p>\n<p>我拍了武汉18点多的天空全景图，云朵就像是上帝（或上帝的孩子）的随手画，缭乱无章，却又十分漂亮。在这里与大家分享。虽然武汉的年均雾霾和空气质量似乎比广州差，但是六月份的武汉天空确实比广州要湛蓝得多，云彩也懒洋洋地徜徉在天空。</p>\n<p>有一本书叫《<a href=\"https://book.douban.com/subject/27624390/\">云彩收集者手册</a>》，由英国赏云协会编制，如果你也喜欢或希望常常抬头仰望遮蔽人类的蓝色天空，不如翻翻这本书吧。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2022/06/29/r4j9FThMy8RJEZt.png\"></p>\n","feature":true,"text":"这段时间我回到了武汉和同学与对象游玩。广州正值雨季，终日天色昏昏、雨水淅沥，而武汉却阳光正盛、热气灼灼。 我拍了武汉18点多的天空全景图，云朵就像是上帝（或上帝的孩子）的随手画，缭乱无章，却又十分漂亮。在这里与大家分享。虽然武汉的年均雾霾和空气质量似乎比广州差，但是六月份的武汉天...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":227,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"生活录","slug":"生活录","count":4,"path":"api/categories/生活录.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"小确幸","slug":"小确幸","count":4,"path":"api/tags/小确幸.json"},{"name":"自然","slug":"自然","count":3,"path":"api/tags/自然.json"}],"toc":"","author":{"name":"桌沿","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/img/me.png","link":"/","description":"桌沿奇思 Newsletter 主理人，少数派签约作者","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"sspai":{"icon":"/svg/sspai.svg","link":"https://sspai.com/u/379wzx2e/posts"},"jike":{"icon":"/svg/jike.svg","link":"https://okjk.co/IktPrE"},"youtube":{"icon":"/svg/youtube.svg","link":"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCDHwHAiT-jJ4AACLHir70Fg"},"twitter":{"icon":"/svg/twitter.svg","link":"https://twitter.com/desksidezhuoyan"},"ins":{"icon":"/svg/instagram.svg","link":"https://www.instagram.com/deskside.zhuoyan/"},"mailto":{"icon":"/svg/mailto.svg","link":"mailto:deskside.zhuoyan@outlook.com"}}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"《iPad mini 6 天生学渣 越用越拉》","uid":"abdfdd58fc80383